Create new OpenGL ES project.

Add lotech/src dir to xcode project, renamed to lotech.

Target -> Get Info -> Build Settings:
    Other C flags: -I lotech -DIOS
    Target Device Family: iPhone/iPad

Rename EAGLView.m -> EAGLView.mm and edit:
    #include "lt.h"

    Add:
        self.multipleTouchEnabled = YES;
    to initWithCoder method (just before "return self;").
